title: Jurassic Park Chaos Island
description:
An old (1997) Real Time Strategy game where you get to control some characters from the movie and some dinosaurs. I found it on eMule so I thought I'd share it here. Compressed in 7zip to shave off 70Mb. I only have 384k upstream so please help me seed.

Works fine with WinXP

---

First run Setup.exe then install the game. Ignore the errors then run CIsland.exe to start the game.
